        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "When she was sure the three boys in the bed were awake and miserable, she crossed the room with a hurried, heavy tread and clumped, clumped down the stairs into the kitchen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
