        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Now hurry along, all of you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "It's quarter to seven.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Eric did not hurry along.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "He threw down his spoon and cried, \"I'd just as soon starve in the streets, and wade in its icy puddles, too, as live here with you and your nasty boys and work in that old canning factory! I just wonder how you'd feel if I went out this morning and never, never came back!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "I'd like to do that!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "You don't want to starve.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "\"You said it wouldn't matter to you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "You won't see me again, any of you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "I hate you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000018_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000018_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "You've made me hate you hard!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "In a minute he was in a flood of people, men, women and children moving towards the canning factory, a big brick building on the outskirts of the city.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Now he had often hated before, but never quite like this.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "So he walked along in the direction the others were going, the hating tears in his eyes and on his face.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "He was walking along with his head up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "It was only waiting for Eric to see it before it would take hold of him and carry him away into happiness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "It had waited for him at the door of the dull, bare little house that had never been home to him, but his tears would not let him see it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "And he did feel,--just in time to let the Magic work.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Eric did not think about being late.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000025_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000025_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "The Magic was pulling him now.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Over the roof of the factory he saw the tops of tall trees waving.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "He had never looked so high above the factory before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Now he saw the tops of the tall trees beckoning him in a golden mist.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000026_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000026_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Still he knew the beckoning was going on behind the mist.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Very slowly, with little firm steps, he went by the factory door, and then around under its windows to the wood at the back.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "It was Indian Summer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Eric dropped his ragged coat and cap on the edge of the wood,--it was so warm,--and went in.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_104382_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/104382/7315_104382_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "Had they sent him, perhaps, to do a different kind of work that could only be done in the woods?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7315_86682_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7315/86682/7315_86682_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "And trews being the vest and breeches united in one piece, and ornamented with fringes, were very comfortable, and suitable to be worn in walking or dancing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
