        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "And again the sprightly tailor replied: \"I see that, but I'll sew this!\" and stitched away at his trews.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
