        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "And still it kept rising through the pavement, until it shook a great pair of arms in the tailor's face, and said: \"Do you see these great arms of mine?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
