        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "He had no sooner got inside the gate, and shut it, than the monster came up to it; and, enraged at losing his prize, struck the wall above the gate, and left there the mark of his five great fingers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
