        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7315",
        "content": "She tried to replace the arm, but it moved with a frightful rigidity which could not deceive a sick nurse. She screamed aloud; then running to the door exclaimed,--\"Help, help!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
